des: Located on Bush River, Water’s Edge Restaurant and Bata Bar offers a full menu of steak, seafood, and light fare from our award-winning Chef Manny. Our Bata Bar Veranda offers breathtaking water views, a nice walk on our pier and the picture perfect sunset. Enjoy a nice evening out with your family or friends in a social distancing, safe environment.
